desc: GreenTeck Global provides eco friendly cleaning solutions which are 100% non toxic, non allergenic, chemical free, natural, safe for skin and safe for the planet. Electrolysed water is a natural bleach alternative which can be used as a glass cleaner, toilet bowl cleaner, air freshener, degreaser and hand sanitiser.
